### List all available metrics
GET http://localhost:8080/actuator/metrics
Accept: application/json


### Total number of HTTP requests per endpoint
GET http://localhost:8080/actuator/metrics/http.server.requests
Accept: application/json





### JVM Memory usage
GET http://localhost:8080/actuator/metrics/jvm.memory.used
Accept: application/json

### JVM Threads (live/peak/daemon)
GET http://localhost:8080/actuator/metrics/jvm.threads.live
Accept: application/json

### JVM GC (garbage collection activity)
GET http://localhost:8080/actuator/metrics/jvm.gc.memory.allocated
Accept: application/json


### Database Connection Pool usage (HikariCP)
GET http://localhost:8080/actuator/metrics/hikaricp.connections.active
Accept: application/json

GET http://localhost:8080/actuator/metrics/hikaricp.connections.max
Accept: application/json

GET http://localhost:8080/actuator/metrics/hikaricp.connections.usage
Accept: application/json


### Application Uptime
GET http://localhost:8080/actuator/metrics/process.uptime
Accept: application/json



